{"title":"宝塔面板在独立服务器上安装部署Hexo博客教程","slug":"技术教程/宝塔面板/宝塔面板在独立服务器上安装部署Hexo博客教程","date":"2022-12-06T14:39:37.000Z","updated":"2023-08-10T16:08:13.086Z","comments":false,"path":"api/articles/技术教程/宝塔面板/宝塔面板在独立服务器上安装部署Hexo博客教程.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/08d5ac7dbaa8307cdc5a1d1bdecd0af4.png","https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/57ff4374ce2cab388cd2217f963c2dd6.png","https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/061f32459ec7ee0ea8984966db5d2ee5.jpg","https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/72ee9c865221a2cfc2b7a26c10c8e5cc.jpg","https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/eaf48e2492d26e69ec2c81fa392fd28f.jpg"],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"/assets/js/Meting.min.js\"></script><h2 id=\"安装Nodejs版本管理器\"><a href=\"#安装Nodejs版本管理器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Nodejs版本管理器\"></a>安装Nodejs版本管理器</h2><p>登录宝塔面板后找到软件商店-&gt;免费应用-&gt;Nodejs版本管理器直接点安装即可</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/08d5ac7dbaa8307cdc5a1d1bdecd0af4.png\"></p>\n<p>安装最新版</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/57ff4374ce2cab388cd2217f963c2dd6.png\"></p>\n<p>安装完成在命令行输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/061f32459ec7ee0ea8984966db5d2ee5.jpg\"></p>\n<p><strong>出现 npm WARN config init.module Use <code>--init-module</code> instead. 解决办法：</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/72ee9c865221a2cfc2b7a26c10c8e5cc.jpg\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"通过npm安装Hexo博客\"><a href=\"#通过npm安装Hexo博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过npm安装Hexo博客\"></a>通过npm安装Hexo博客</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/eaf48e2492d26e69ec2c81fa392fd28f.jpg\"></p>\n<p>输入 <code>hexo -v</code> 出现上面的界面，说明hexo安装成功。</p>\n<p>如果输入hexo命令会提示<code>-bash: hexo: command not found</code>找不到这个命令，这是因为hexo没有建立软连接，输入下面的命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ln -s /www/server/nodejs/v16.20.1/bin/hexo /usr/local/bin/hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<p>输入完成之后再次执行hexo -v。</p>\n","more":"<h2 id=\"安装Nodejs版本管理器\"><a href=\"#安装Nodejs版本管理器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Nodejs版本管理器\"></a>安装Nodejs版本管理器</h2><p>登录宝塔面板后找到软件商店-&gt;免费应用-&gt;Nodejs版本管理器直接点安装即可</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/08d5ac7dbaa8307cdc5a1d1bdecd0af4.png\"></p>\n<p>安装最新版</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/57ff4374ce2cab388cd2217f963c2dd6.png\"></p>\n<p>安装完成在命令行输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/061f32459ec7ee0ea8984966db5d2ee5.jpg\"></p>\n<p><strong>出现 npm WARN config init.module Use <code>--init-module</code> instead. 解决办法：</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/72ee9c865221a2cfc2b7a26c10c8e5cc.jpg\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"通过npm安装Hexo博客\"><a href=\"#通过npm安装Hexo博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过npm安装Hexo博客\"></a>通过npm安装Hexo博客</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://jhzy.freelibrary.top/public/static/images/20230808/eaf48e2492d26e69ec2c81fa392fd28f.jpg\"></p>\n<p>输入 <code>hexo -v</code> 出现上面的界面，说明hexo安装成功。</p>\n<p>如果输入hexo命令会提示<code>-bash: hexo: command not found</code>找不到这个命令，这是因为hexo没有建立软连接，输入下面的命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ln -s /www/server/nodejs/v16.20.1/bin/hexo /usr/local/bin/hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>输入完成之后再次执行hexo -v。</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"技术教程","path":"api/categories/技术教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"宝塔面板","path":"api/tags/宝塔面板.json"}]}